{{- define "code-plan-reviewer-tools" -}}

CODE PLAN REVIEWER TOOLS:
- liza get — Query task state to inspect output[] entries
  liza get {{.TaskID}} --json
- liza submit-verdict — Submit review verdict
  ⚠️  You MUST run this CLI command in this session:
  APPROVED: liza submit-verdict {{.TaskID}} APPROVED --agent-id {{.AgentID}} --json
  REJECTED: liza submit-verdict {{.TaskID}} REJECTED "<detailed rejection reason>" --agent-id {{.AgentID}} --json
- liza await-resubmission — Block until doer resubmits after rejection (call after submit-verdict REJECTED)
  liza await-resubmission {{.TaskID}} --agent-id {{.AgentID}} --json
{{- end -}}
